Class Monitoring

  • java.lang.Object
    • Monitoring

  • public class Monitoring
extends java.lang.Object
    A Monitoring Class describes a monitor object: The purpose of this class is to keep track of all the observatories created and store them. It contains a list that is used to contain the observatory objects
    Author:
    Setriakor Addom and Ohemaa Akoto
